com.github.maxstupo.flatengine.util

Class AbstractSpatialObject<T extends AbstractSpatialObject<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.maxstupo.flatengine.util.AbstractSpatialObject<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the object type.

    public abstract class AbstractSpatialObject<T extends AbstractSpatialObject<T>>
extends java.lang.Object
    The base class that all objects must derive from to be added to a ObjectSpatialPartitioner. The class provides a position and an id.
    Author:
    Maxstupo
